Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『飛吧！GUNDAM』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第3班的人，請到餐廳用膳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.56,0:02:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，要去叫阿姆羅呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.03,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.22,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.81,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你發燒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼疲倦還是不要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從在衛星7號逃亡後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就從未好好的休息過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我現在感覺很倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是還睡不著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要雪拉看看呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像學過點醫學呢！是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳別麻煩我好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要適可宜止啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點不似平時的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不停的在機動戰士內作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不似平時的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次戰爭那些大人大半也犧牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只靠少年人及老人來支持大局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.28,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信聯邦和ZION也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別咬手指！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎聯邦軍將我們當做魚餌...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魚餌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍一定在開發新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這段期間就將我們作餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吸引敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是這樣的！我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別亂想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是先休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為你留起食物好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人！還未聯絡到總部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有無線電來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參謀總部嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.49,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總部，這裏是母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請將通信由M轉去Z路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z路線嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望母艦可以衝出敵軍包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向著大海方向走出去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就祇有這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連如何支持也沒提及？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...我們不可和總部通話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在敵軍範圍用暗號通信己很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參謀本部是如何想的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們根本不知什麼是戰場！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人家們的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然啊！我們又沒法找到證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說！以為我在收起自己吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你的面色會比我們好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何以阿姆羅和良的膳食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會在份量上多出那麼多的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是布萊特的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是要將倆人當作正規軍看待！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是只有他們去打仗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.45,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍人的食物是以工作量計算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.75,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的事可以和隊長說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會理我呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅哥，我給你一樣東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.29,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓人知道呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.21,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦的武器和彈藥快用盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次敵人來還可捱得住嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也知道！所以正在想法子呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想生存下去，還不簡單！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要放棄White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然這麼想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別放在心上啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起吃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎樣好意思啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你不吃怎可以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便別叫我在這裏吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做有什麼後果呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以一直戰至今日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算也有一點成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也培養出單獨作戰的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，破爛的地方大致上修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人和雪拉去那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在調整瞄準器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找人出去巡邏一下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你去做巡邏工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來控制室吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼！上來啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，快些上來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巡邏工作不必我去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我己經要時常作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅實在很倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們亦太過依懶他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是由我和隼人出去巡邏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部交給計算機控制！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！正打算這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！現在先將部計算機調好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要它跟著我便成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪，其實你不需要去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要向姊姊交待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有家人的你是不會明白的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員準備出發攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵軍戰鬥機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪，立即停止攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就去擊落他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回來，卡爾瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，費了不少努力才發現敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不立即攻擊呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們有6架核戰機早攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是30秒前的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過只是一架巡邏機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來木馬正十分焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,焦急？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是第一次派出巡邏機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.01,0:09:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有弱點所以才想知我們動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得有點道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不必去理會那巡邏機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該立即攻擊母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！去追蹤敵軍的巡邏機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，準備將核戰機安裝到鋼坦克及鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要入去鐵棺材裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坐到上面去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，拜託了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要早給我指示呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你會瞭解我的心情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連凱也用鋼加農出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也下定決心去作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快大家就會不想去的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他們不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被命令出去很多次的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？芙勞·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說他不想去作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在要應戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以保證我作戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來可好好睡一覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.69,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保證？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實我自己也不知該怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.03,0:10:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道..若沒有阿姆羅你去作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一早已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也早死了..不過..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事實在太恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平安降落...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.68,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.29,0:11:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就只有這點軍力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM就快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打仗要有信心才可取勝，對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉小姐真是善於幫別人壯膽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你為何不出動完成任務？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問隊長為什麼而要去打仗呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在根本沒時間跟你講哲學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快起來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真想GUNDAM出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何不自己來駕駛呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我會駕駛，我早做了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一樣，並不是因為會才要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你打我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打你有什麼不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己想清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在大發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以發洩得了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為我是個沒出息的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那面又來了一隊敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你要小心啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.38,0:12:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你叫我別太過前進？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，這地方較空曠，要小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白敵軍出了什麼問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了！為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然現在有兩個陸戰型出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但最利害的卻沒出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看多數是故障！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由現在起你別插手看我的手段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打敗他們給你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會好好見識你的高明攻擊法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將攻擊的目標定在左引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克，鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍正在集中火力攻擊左引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這班傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打了我兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸也從來未動過手打我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才會任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未經教訓的人是不會長大過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會去，就算是以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會再去駕駛GUNDAM的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你講說話要適可而止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要振作過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說那些無情的話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！如果你還要任性下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是一個沒出息的廢物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來我以為你很有天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會勝過夏亞，可以打敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你太令我失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得你有本駕駛GUNDAM的說明書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去駕駛GUNDAM！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最討厭沒有自信的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是不敢說要保護母艦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你不是男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.67,0:14:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM並不是容易駕駛的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我仍不忿氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我是男子漢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你去那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.46,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，敵人只攻擊母艦，快回防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只得兩架機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若沒有對空炮火的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就打不中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著，別理嘍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集中攻擊木馬的左邊引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧，跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.82,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵機正全力攻擊左引擎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有辦法對付他們嗎？阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有個新的戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請叫鋼坦克和鋼加農掩護我好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會通知他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪上校的攻擊法看來相當高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎他並不是光靠父母的威望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以升高官的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，我們只看不幫手可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的，假如要幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自會通知我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校的自尊心很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好反而會被他痛罵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這個距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信無線電是可以接收到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！雖然粒子的濃度依然很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在的距離通信是沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以聯絡的話就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上我也不願意被卡爾瑪上校罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個機動戰士終於也出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終也是陸戰用的武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二小隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即攻擊白色機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就想打敗我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實GUNDAM是藏著彈跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和火箭式的衝力系統的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！機動戰士會飛的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM竟可在空中作戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.08,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用無線電叫坦克及激光火炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在GUNDAM落地之前掩護他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別令他讓人襲擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克，鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以見到GUNDAM嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到阿姆羅這麼利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不讓飛機低飛是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會給你們飛低過一尺的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,8、5、0...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那機動戰士會跳高的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，是在飛行呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍竟然有這種機動戰士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，真想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅會有這種高飛的戰術呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，是那傢伙的優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然口中說不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍然和敵人周旋到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你變堅強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第6架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著第7架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第7架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這隻怪物，掉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快給我掉下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛！聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.29,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在將那機動戰士引過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待他入到射程範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即開火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你逃的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還不知快進入野牛的射程呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛，快將他轟下來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.79,0:19:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.13,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.15,0:19:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪上校啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.53,0:19:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？我的確在發出訊號啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聯邦的運輸機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊的機動戰士，你聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山中是埋有野牛的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回White Base吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會知的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電線鬆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然會引致接觸不良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技師長準備接受懲罰處分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該在屏幕看到我作戰的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我沒通知你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也應該想辦法來協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.89,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為我怕傷了你的自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怕傷害我的自尊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你叫我別插手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我亦瞭解到像你這樣的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是輕微損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定可以在下次彌補到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過最可惜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是當我要擊落聯邦軍運輸機時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校就在射程的直線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我無法攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！你明白便好了！夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉和密斯號來的隊員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與及病人一共35人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都願意收留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於White Base則沒有任何指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要維持原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外到目前的戰鬥紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於雷比爾將軍的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請給我們一份影印本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.51,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但瑪吉露達少尉，我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.61,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼White Base要維持原狀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.62,0:21:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過雷比爾將軍認為母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以戰下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.79,0:21:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以撥入正規軍行列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為現在的聯邦軍內部正一團糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這次來，是奉了雷比爾將軍之命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和參謀本部是沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.90,0:22:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會再給我們援助嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開ZION軍的勢力範圍後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者可以的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.98,0:22:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別忘記聯邦軍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍有人關心你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有你這樣英勇的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.66,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也早就死了，很多謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.19,0:22:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能你是個超能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.20,0:22:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.40,0:22:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.61,0:22:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉留下一陣香味便走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.59,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿姆羅來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是初次體會女性的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.17,0:23:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒能打下White Base也就無法和伊榭蓮娜相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.20,0:23:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪·薩比展開最後的突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當阿姆羅他們在黑暗中看到恐懼時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞的陰謀籠罩了卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『卡爾瑪之死』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

